                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                ".The overall uncertainty associated with each",
                "experimental point varied from 10% to 17%, depending",
                "on the number of counts in the elastic peak at each",
                "angle."
              ]
            },
            {
